{"tid":190571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普 指長遠要同中國建立良好關係  更讚揚習夫人是出色的歌唱家 但暗示","createTime":"2017-04-07T08:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T08:05:36.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa6dd7d6570af575a5758c7c322621344374827","tid":190571,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:05:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Donald Trump predicts &quot;very great&quot; relationship but jokes he's gotten nothing from Xi so far.</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPresident Donald Trump predicted a &ldquo;very great&rdquo; relationship with China&rsquo;s Xi Jinping as the pair met for the first time at his Florida resort of Mar-a-Lago Thursday, when cordiality replaced tough anti-China rhetoric.<br />\n<br />\nTrump, in his signature red tie, warmly welcomed his Chinese counterpart Xi, decked out in contrasting blue, to what the US leader likes to call the &ldquo;Winter White House&rdquo; for a superpower summit in the sun.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/170407093846-xt-trump-meet-1-exlarge-169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.cdn.cnn.com%2Fcnnnext%2Fdam%2Fassets%2F170407093846-xt-trump-meet-1-exlarge-169.jpg&h=064e6c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/78/590x/Donald-Trump-Xi-Jinping-handshake-Florida-788956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F78%2F590x%2FDonald-Trump-Xi-Jinping-handshake-Florida-788956.jpg&h=6ce8574f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/07/154423_ade5478be2be64bb42a707b862b34f0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F07%2F154423_ade5478be2be64bb42a707b862b34f0b.jpg&h=eeb0e79d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}